The paper discusses the need for a modern computing paradigm to address issues encountered under extreme computing conditions. This suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-category of cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), which deals with new and innovative computing technologies. Additionally, the paper mentions the need to explain new phenomena and enhance computing features, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.AR (Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality) or cs.SE (Software Engineering). The proposal of a new computing paradigm also suggests a focus on programming languages and systems, which could place the paper in the sub-category of cs.PL (Programming Languages) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
